1) In order to fix Bd S_wave in the fit, I made the changes below in CreateAmplitudes(self) in PDF_2012_Asym.py:
Before
**********
if not "As2" in dir(self):
self.As2 = RooRealVar("As2"+name,"As2"+name,0.05, 0,0.3)

Now
**********
if namephys== "Bd":
self.As2=RooRealVar("As2"+namephys,"As2"+namephys,1.60099e-02)# this value is taken from the previous fit
else:
self.As2 = RooRealVar("As2"+namephys,"As2"+namephys,0.05, 0,0.3)

Results compatible with previous ones, here:
http://marwww.in2p3.fr/~kanso/jpsiK/results_fix_AsBd.txt
