2) Since Bd->K* & Bs->K*bar so we should add A_D & Aprod_s with different signs in both cases

Before:
***********
$ns-2011p =(nBs2011p_{phys})*(1 + A_D +Aprod_s)$
$nd-2011n =(nBd2011n_{phys})*(1 - A_D - Aprod_s)$
$nd-2011p = (nBd2011p_{phys})*(1 + A_D + Aprod_s)$

Now:
********
$ns-2011p =(nBs2011p_{phys})*(1 + A_D -Aprod_s)$
$nd-2011n = (nBd2011n_{phys})*(1 + A_D - Aprod_s)$
$nd-2011p = (nBd2011p_{phys})*(1 - A_D + Aprod_d)$

With :
$Aprod_s = -\kappa_{s}A^P(\Bs)=-0.00132$
$Aprod_d =-\kappa_{d}A^P(\Bd)= 0.00030$
$A_D = -0.01185$

N.B: Equations & values taken from B2hh analysis. 

